\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><html lang=\"en\"><header class=\"bg-white shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-20 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/en\"><img src=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-5.png\" alt=\"SafetyLink\" class=\"h-10 w-auto\"/></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8\"><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en\">Home</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en/solutions\">Solutions</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en/services\">Services</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en/about\">About</a><a class=\"text-[#333] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/en/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"bg-primary text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] transition-colors\" href=\"/en/contact\">Request Demo</a><a class=\"text-[#686868] font-medium text-sm hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"https://app.safetylink.ai\">Login</a><a class=\"text-xs text-navy font-semibold bg-[#eef3ff] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\" href=\"/es\">ES</a></nav><button class=\"lg:hidden text-navy p-2\" aria-label=\"Menu\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"bg-navy text-white py-20 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4\">Safety Link: The Most Legally Defensible Safety Platform</h1><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8 italic max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Protect your people, protect your business, protect your future — without bloated costs or guesswork.</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] shadow-[0_2px_6px_0_rgba(0,183,55,0.25)] transition-all \" href=\"/contact\">Start with a Free Consult</a></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Guided by former OSHA leadership and delivered by OSHA‑authorized trainers</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Bilingual (English/Spanish) by default — platform UI, content, and support</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Site‑specific programs (not generic templates) – policies tailored to each job site</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Legally defensible documentation, advised by OSHA attorneys</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>Mobile‑first + offline mode – audits, inspections, photos, GPS, timestamps without internet</div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span>SMB pricing with enterprise power – scalable, affordable compliance</div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255,255,255) 0%, rgb(244,243,242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Built‑In Capabilities (Out‑of‑the‑Box)</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Built‑in LMS (SCORM 1.2)</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Interactive, role‑based courses with quizzes &amp; certificates; mapped to Training Matrix</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Full bilingual delivery</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">UI, training content, and support in English &amp; Spanish</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Site‑specific policies</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Client/job‑site‑level policies, version control, acknowledgments</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Digital signatures &amp; acknowledgments</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Audit‑ready trails, exports</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Corrective Actions automation</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Follow‑ups, due dates, proof‑of‑correction, escalation</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Real‑time dashboards &amp; AI insights</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Surface overdue training, failed items, open CAPAs, trend risks</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Contractor portal &amp; access controls</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Role‑ and site‑based permissions, separation of duties</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Mobile‑first offline mode</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Full functionality without signal</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]\"><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Affordable SMB pricing</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs leading-relaxed\">Tiered pricing, enterprise‑grade capability when needed</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-2\">Comparison: Safety Link vs Generic Tools</h2><p class=\"text-primary text-center font-semibold mb-8 italic\">Other tools check boxes. We close risk.</p><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b-2 border-navy\"><th class=\"text-left py-3 text-navy\">Feature</th><th class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">Other Tools</th><th class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">Safety Link</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Bilingual (EN/ES) default</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Site‑specific programs</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">OSHA‑Authorized trainers</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Former OSHA leadership on staff</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Expert support &amp; consultations</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Legally defensible documentation</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">On‑site audit support</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-100\"><td class=\"py-3 text-[#333]\">Affordable for SMBs</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-[#666]\">✗</td><td class=\"text-center py-3 text-primary font-bold\">✓</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255,255,255) 0%, rgb(244,243,242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Two Deployment Paths</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]\"><div class=\"h-40 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/software-tablet-BSMxY2uI.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Safety Software</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-4\">Run training, audits/inspections, incidents, CAPA, OSHA logs, and analytics in one platform. Designed for SMBs seeking control without spreadsheets.</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] shadow-[0_2px_6px_0_rgba(0,183,55,0.25)] transition-all \" href=\"/contact\">Explore Software</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]\"><div class=\"h-40 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/program-team-BDtLA316.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Program Management</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm mb-4\">OSHA‑authorized professionals design and implement site‑specific programs, conduct audits, train teams, and keep you inspection‑ready — ideal for high‑risk or multi‑site operations.</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-white text-navy px-9 py-3.5 rounded-[10px] font-medium text-sm shadow-[rgba(0,0,0,0.3)_0px_0px_1px_0px] hover:shadow-md transition-all \" href=\"/safety-program-management\">Explore Program Management</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">What Makes Safety Link the Gold Standard</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">1</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">OSHA‑Authorized Expertise</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Former OSHA leadership and labor attorneys guide the platform; supervisor sign‑offs and full audit trails ensure legal defensibility.</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">2</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Process‑First Architecture</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Every module (onboarding → training → CAPA) is interconnected so nothing falls through.</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">3</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Proof Built In</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Geo‑tagging, time stamps, version‑controlled policies, e‑signatures, and printable auditor‑ready reports.</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">4</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Performance in the Field</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Responsive mobile, offline mode, photo/video capture, GPS, digital signatures.</p></div><div class=\"text-center p-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-xl font-bold\">5</div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Scales Without Sticker Shock</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm leading-relaxed\">Start at SMB scale; add multi‑site oversight, contractor controls, and advanced analytics as you grow.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255,255,255) 0%, rgb(244,243,242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Feature Highlights</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_5_feature-mobile-BeQJutVM.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Mobile‑Ready + Offline</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Access safety tools anywhere, without internet</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_6_feature-audits-Chwoapsm.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Audits &amp; Inspections</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Real‑time site audits, track findings</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_7_feature-training-DlajBew5.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Training (SCORM)</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Full LMS with bilingual SCORM course support</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_8_feature-quizzes-BN4TbLCR.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Quizzes &amp; Certificates</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Verify comprehension, auto‑generate certificates</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/feature-policies-q899d3JL.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Site‑Specific Policies</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Tailored to your hazards and sites</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_10_feature-workflow-CfUrGWrp.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Corrective Actions Workflow</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Track issues from identification to resolution</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_11_feature-dashboard-H-FS-km3.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Compliance Dashboards &amp; KPIs</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Real‑time visibility into safety performance</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_12_feature-contractor-CBU_fgsQ.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Contractor Portal &amp; Access Controls</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Role‑based permissions for external workers</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_4px_15px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_28px_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-shadow\"><div class=\"h-44 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_13_feature-affordable-DzRtQ8Ac.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-5\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy text-sm mb-1\">Affordable for SMBs</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-xs\">Enterprise features without enterprise pricing</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-10\">How It Works</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold\">1</div><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Assess &amp; Audit</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">Bilingual, site‑specific reviews uncover risks before OSHA does.</p></div><div><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold\">2</div><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Implement</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">Build your English/Spanish program, launch training and workflows.</p></div><div><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl font-bold\">3</div><h3 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">Track &amp; Improve</h3><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">Dashboards, AI alerts, CAPA, and logs keep you inspection‑ready.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy text-center mb-10\">Built for SMBs and High‑Risk Enterprises</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-48 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/imgi_14_smb-teamwork-BfplCzdt.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">Small &amp; Mid‑Market Teams</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm\">Enterprise‑grade safety without large invoices. Launch fast, manage simply.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"h-48 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;/images/enterprise-growth-CxBH0X1y.jpg&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-navy mb-2\">High‑Risk Enterprises</h3><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm\">Multi‑site controls, advanced analytics, contractor oversight, litigation‑ready evidence.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-10\">Safety That Moves the Numbers</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2\">15–35%</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">fewer injuries with well‑run IIPP programs</p></div><div><p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2\">$170B+</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">annual U.S. injury costs – protect your P&amp;L</p></div><div><p class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-2\">Up to 6×</p><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm\">ROI on safety investments</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-8\">Industries Served</h2><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3\"><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Manufacturing</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Construction</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Healthcare &amp; Hospitals</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Energy &amp; Utilities / Oil, Gas</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Government &amp; Public Sector</span><span class=\"bg-[#f9fafb] text-navy font-semibold text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl hover:bg-navy hover:text-white transition-all\">Transportation &amp; Logistics</span></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-6\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(rgb(255,255,255) 0%, rgb(244,243,242) 100%)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4\">Ready to protect your people and your business?</h2><p class=\"text-[#666] text-lg mb-8\">Talk to an OSHA Authorized Advisor</p><a class=\"inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rou